  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Chalet Belina is an attractive chalet apartment on the second floor of the Ourson building, where we run three chalets with our sister company Esprit, each chalet has their individual host who will look after you throughout the week. The chalet sleeps up to twelve people, so it is ideal for a group of family and friends travelling to <a data-udi="umb://document/4c93b881bd494483871697b278b37899" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4c93b881bd494483871697b278b37899}" title="La Rosière">La Rosiere</a>. Chalet Belina is shared with our sister company Esprit Ski specialising in family ski holidays and childcare.<span></span></p>
<h2>Perfect location</h2>
<p>If you like hitting the slopes as early as possible and getting back in time for the après ski, you'll benefit choosing this catered ski chalet. Located 50 metres from the ski lifts and less than 300 metres from the resort centre of La Rosiere, you'll be able to get on and off the slopes with ease and be able to make the most of the resort amenities.</p>
<h2>Ideal for sole occupancy groups </h2>
<p>With three attractive bedrooms and the possibility to accommodate up to 12 people, invite your family and your friends  to spend a week in this cosy chalet. The warm and welcoming lounge-dining room has incredible views across the resort, and is a great spot to catch up with your family and friends with a bit of cake and a coffee after a day on the slopes. Each room can accommodate up to four people, with additional twin or bunk beds in a separate area - making this chalet an ideal choice for groups looking for a sole occupancy chalet.</p>
<h2>Family friendly</h2>
<p><span>Chalet Belina is perfect for families, it is shared with our sister company Esprit Ski who specialise in family skiing holidays and childcare. La Rosiere is one of Esprit's main hubs for childcare, which can include infant care, Snow Club, Xtra lessons and Mountain Academy. Children booked into Esprit children’s ski lessons will be collected by our Esprit Rangers from the chalet and taken to the ski school meeting place. When booking this chalet with Inghams you can book your children into our Esprit childcare, just give our Reservations team a call to book. </span><span></span></p>
<h3><span>Our chalets are going greener, so our mountains don't</span></h3>
<p>Our menu is changing for the better. In all of our chalets we're giving you more choice, with both meat-free and meat options on offer throughout your stay. This is driven as part of our commitment to reduce our <a rel="noopener" data-udi="umb://document/67e40dbb55ff45098496ea2e7eee1f72" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/about-us/sustainability" target="_blank" title="Sustainability">carbon footprint</a>.</p>]]></description>
