  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Accommodation Summary</strong></p>
<p>The Chalet Belina is on the second floor of the Ourson building, where we along with our sister company Esprit, run three chalets, each with an individual host. The second floor has the chalet entrance to lounge and dining area with fireplace, TV and balcony with mountain views.</p>
<p><strong>Suite 1 (sleeps 3-4)</strong>: Double room with balcony and twin bunks room under the eaves, with shower and wc</p>
<p><strong>Suite 2 (sleeps 4):</strong> Twin room with shower and separate wc and door leading to double room with bath and balcony </p>
<p><strong>Suite 3 (sleeps 4):</strong> Double room with balcony and shower and twin room with shower, sharing a separate wc from the connecting hallway</p>
<p>All suites will take a cot and all the showers are new walk-in showers.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
